h2 Test RESTful Service 
	a(href='http://www.crummy.com/writing/speaking/2008-QCon/act3.html') Richardson Maturity 
	span Level 2

i(style="color:gray")
	ul
		li Many URI's, each supporting multiple HTTP methods
		li The best example is Amazon S3
		
p(style="color:red") Gentle WARNING: Not all options are operational yet!!

ol(id="toc")
	li
		a(href='/rtests/levels/0')
			span Level 0
	li
		a(href="/rtests/levels/1")
			span Level 1
			
	li(class='current')
		a(href="/rtests/levels/2")
			span Level 2
	li
